Description:
You are about to get to the vanguard group. They are giving it all on their fight against an impressive war machine and the general that commands it. But they don’t seem able to last much longer.

A reinforcement group is on its way to support the dwarven general, but they have to move at the pace of their own war machine, a model you never seen before.

You need to do something! The group can barely hold against one war machine, another one would be devastating.
DescriptionAction: You are not going to let those reinforcements arrive its target.
